data.description: Welcome to this spacious city row home that has just been freshly painted, giving it a clean and inviting feel. With 5 bedrooms, and large rooms it offers plenty of room for your family and guests.  One of the standout features of this property is the balcony on both the 2nd and 3rd floors, providing you with a perfect spot to relax and enjoy the city views. It also has a newer roof and has been converted to gas.  This home is not only spacious but also conveniently located in the heart of the city, giving you easy access to all the amenities and attractions the city has to offer. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make it your own!
